name: ethylenediaminetetraacetate,FMNH2:O2 oxidoreductase (glyoxylate-forming)
definition: Ethylenediaminetriacetic acid + Reduced FMN + Oxygen <=> Ethylenediamine-N,N'-diacetic acid + Glyoxylate + FMN + H2O
comment: second step of two-step reaction (see R11456, R11454+R11455)
